{"tid":1475480,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"818 就算政府點樣反對 香港人都要企出黎","createTime":"2019-08-15T13:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:53:13.000Z","uid":305408,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"30efe50cb088533fc20592b8318894085193ef9f","tid":1475480,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:25:28.000Z","msg":"我地一向既行動就係對抗政府<br />\n希望各位對自己身邊既和理非可以宣傳下 ,不論係親朋戚友 , 老定嫩 <br />\n唔好因為無不反對通知書就唔出黎<br />\n從來我地最大既武器就係人數 , 唔係我地所謂既GEAR<br />\n大家可以用自己既經驗去引導佢地<br />\n例如: 次次港島遊行都係會去到金鐘 / 中聯辦附近先有狗之類<br />\n<br />\n唔可以話係最後一次 但我地一定要俾政府知道 香港人係唔會因為佢既暴政而跪低<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可 <br />\n光復香港。時代革命<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8e713ac79c3e6dd0fe76c583db5d83378657ad42","tid":1475480,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:26:53.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"727f08c24d36bbe251dae9e855a5e07ee2c8fbfa","tid":1475480,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"716ab76cdc984ebb4e4555ac7a296250916a2944","tid":1475480,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:29:30.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"22b470151d63aa63522309c0ad5bd050a9a2b6e3","tid":1475480,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"b394d8e89ef8079b9ff8f1da076ba4fa84525534","tid":1475480,"uid":76922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GkK6vjT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGkK6vjT.jpg&h=faa81d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAOOJET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAOOJET.jpg&h=3b098cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R1rsZde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.